OCRmyPDF GUI Client
===================

This application is a derivative work that provides a graphical user interface 
for OCRmyPDF functionality.

Copyright Notice
================
This project incorporates and depends on OCRmyPDF:

OCRmyPDF
Copyright (c) 2022 James R. Barlow and contributors
Licensed under Mozilla Public License Version 2.0
Source: https://github.com/ocrmypdf/OCRmyPDF

OCRmyPDF adds an optical character recognition (OCR) text layer to scanned 
PDF documents, allowing them to be searched.

